SGBVHighlights.project: Protection and Assistance programme for Refugees and IDPs in Duhok-Iraq - IDPs - GBV Unit
SGBVHighlights.summary: Harikar with the support of UNHCR conducted different activities in Sep 2021 for Syrian and Non-Syrian refugees in camps and out of camps such as: case management, awareness sessions, GBV prevention and response training. In addition, CLC-Managers have attended camp coordination meeting as well as protection meeting. Further more, Assisstant Project Manager has attended GBV WG meeting, PSEA Duhok task force, PSEA Iraq network and GBVIMS via online modalities and during the meeting Harikar updates and activities have been shared with attendess.
